/a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p>该 <strong><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></strong> 方法返回的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStream</code></a> 是一个实时视频捕获的画布。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">MediaStream = canvas.captureStream(frameRate);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"framerate\"><code>frameRate</code> 可选</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>设置双精准度浮点值为每个帧的捕获速率。如果未设置，则每次画布更改时都会捕获一个新帧。如果设置为<code>0</code>，则会捕获单个帧。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>对一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> 对象的引用。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">//获取所需要截取媒体流的 canvas element</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvasElt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//截取到媒体流</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> stream <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvasElt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">captureStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 25 FPS</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//使用媒体流</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// E.g.使用 RTCPeerConnection 来传输给其它的电脑</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 下面的 pc 是其他地方创建的一个 RTCPeerConnection</span>\npc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stream<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#dom-htmlcanvaselement-capturestream","title":"Media Capture from DOM Elements"}],"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"看看其他","title":"看看其他","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStream</code></a>,所属接口。</li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLMediaElement.captureStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, 允许从一个媒体中获取流</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API\"><code>Media Capture and Streams API</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"看看其他","id":"看看其他"}],"summary":"该 HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream() 方法返回的 CanvasCaptureMediaStream 是一个实时视频捕获的画布。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/capturestream","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/capturestream/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/